headline: 99% of tech startups are not investible
description:
Most tech founders never accept this fact and continue to chase investors, wasting endless hours of time that could be spent on building and growing your business.

Thanks to https://skilledup.life, now you can accelerate with free talent.

We ourselves are not investible. SkilledUp Life is built by our own free talent.

Now with 11,458 free talent pool from 92 countries, with Africans and notably Nigerians taking the lead.
headline_zh-Hans: 99%的科技初创企业不具备可投资性
headline_zh-Hant: 99%的科技初創企業不具備可投資性

感谢https://skilledup.life，现在你可以用免费的人才来加速。

我们自己是不可投资的。SkilledUp Life是由我们自己的免费人才建立的。

现在有来自92个国家的11,458名免费人才库，其中非洲人，特别是尼日利亚人处于领先地位。
